                          month</span
                        ></span
                      >
                      <span
                        x-show="duration === 'annual'"
                        style="display: none;"
                      >
                        annually</span
                      >
                      <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-500"
                        >USD + Local taxes</Text
